Welcome to Technicity! This tutorial will guide you step-by-step through the basics. Use the left joystick to move and your headset to look around.
First, try to grab the Hammer by pressing the Grip.

Welcome to Technicity! We can start by performing the tutorials first. Using the joystick on your Left Controller, proceed to the tables and perform the Missions need to accomplish. First, try to grab the Hammer by pressing the Trigger.
